OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with any early morning
OL,6,Fcloud soon burning off to leave a warm
OL,7,Fday with sunny spells. Feeling fresher
OL,8,Fon the east coast with sea breezes.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA fine end to the day and
OL,11,Fstaying dry overnight. Low cloud and
OL,12,FHaar could develop around some North
OL,13,FSea coasts.
OL,14,
OL,15,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright and
OL,16,Fwarm or very warm inland. Low cloud
OL,17,Fand Haar could affect North Sea coasts
OL,18,Fand heavy showers perhaps breaking out
OL,19,Flater in the day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
